[[馬爾他|馬爾他]]首次遞交[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的[[奧斯卡最佳國際影片獎|最佳國際影片獎]]，是在2014年的第一次。<ref name="87th">{{cite web |url=http://www.maltatoday.com.mt/arts/film/44775/simshar_for_oscar_foreign_language_film_nominations#.VDeHI40g_30 |title=Simshar vies for Oscar foreign language film nominations |accessdate=10 October 2014 |work=Malta Today}}</ref>奧斯卡最佳外語片獎由[[美國電影藝術與科學學院|美國電影藝術與科學學院]]頒發，為[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]中頒發給年度美國以外最佳非英語電影的獎項<ref name="Rules">{{cite web | title = Rule Thirteen: Special Rules for the Foreign Language Film Award | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts、Sciences | publisher = [[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts、Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts、Sciences]] | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | accessdate = 2013-08-26}}</ref>。該獎項原名為「奧斯卡最佳外語片獎」，但學院認為「外語」該詞已過時，所以於2019年4月更名為「最佳國際影片獎」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archive-date=2019-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527181952/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=ACADEMY ANNOUNCES RULES FOR 92ND OSCARS |url=https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Oscars.org {{!}} Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |date=2019-04-23 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=options |first1=Show more sharing |last2=URLCopied! |first2=Copy Link |title=Film academy is setting new inclusion standards for Oscars eligibility |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2020-06-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Lawler |first1=Kelly |title=Academy to implement diversity standards for Oscars eligibility, set best picture at 10 nominees |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=USA TODAY}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12}}</ref>。

